Description:

	A programming to solving summation puzzles.  Will take two words
	and a proposed summation word.  Program checks if there is a sequence
	of numbers that match letters which sums accordingly to the numbers 
	representing the summation word.  If there exists at least one solution
	every possible permutation that matches a solution pattern is printed.
	If there are no solutions, a message to that effect is printed.  There
	is one class and about a dozen member functions.  The user enters three
	words and solutions are printed.